// Semantic direction:
// innholdsmoderasjon screens user-generated content before it reaches other players.
// tekst_sjekk sends chat text through the mod_leverandør and returns tekst_resultat.
// tekst_score is a per-category confidence value (0–1); above a threshold the text is flagget.
// tekst_blokkert prevents delivery and notifies the sender without exposing the reason.
// bilde_moderasjon applies the same pipeline to player-uploaded avatars and screenshots.
// bruker_rapport lets players flag specific incidents for human review.
// rapport_bevis attaches the flagged message ID, screenshot, or replay segment.
// auto_mute_terskel silences a player automatically after N reports within a window.
// blokkert_sjekk prevents blocked players from appearing in each other's chat or lobby.
// juks_detektor compares client-reported actions against server_autoritets_validering.
// statistikk_anomali flags players whose win rate, accuracy, or speed exceeds plausible bounds.
// ban_system records the infraction, issues a ban_varighet, and notifies the player.
// ban_appell creates a review ticket for human moderators.
// filter_kontekst uses surrounding words to reduce false positives (e.g. medical terms).
// filter_nivå allows servers to configure how aggressively chat is filtered.
// profil_under_18 restricts communication and social features for minors.
// fcos_modus (Family-friendly Content Only Safe) enables the strictest content filtering.
// comm_begrensning limits who can message a protected account (friends only, nobody).

// Primitive flow:
// chat melding: tekst_sjekk(melding) -> tekst_score per kategori
//   > terskel: tekst_flagget -> chat_filter.erstatt | tekst_blokkert
//   < terskel: lever melding til mottakere
// bruker_rapport: rapport_opprett(type, mål_id, bevis)
//   -> rapport_send til moderasjonsserver -> rapport_status = venter
//   human review: rapport_løst -> evt ban_bruker
// anti_juks: per ramme: server_autoritets_validering(klient_input, server_tilstand)
//   avvik > terskel -> statistikk_anomali -> ban_system(type_midlertidig)
// foreldrekontroll: les profil_under_18 -> comm_begrensning(venner_kun)
//   -> kjøp_begrensning(krever_pin) -> fcos_modus(aktiv)

// This defines content moderation and player safety: text/image screening, report system,
// mute/block, anti-cheat with bans, chat filtering, and parental controls.
